# Apptly environment variables
#
# Most config lives next to the package that needs it, NOT here:
#   - Extension (client):  extension/.env    -> VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY (pk_...)
#   - Backend (server):    backend/.dev.vars  -> CLERK_SECRET_KEY (sk_...)
# BYO-key users paste their LLM API key into the extension UI
# (stored in browser.storage.local), not into any .env file.
#
# Never commit a real .env file. Only this .env.example is tracked.

# --- Hosted LLM proxy (future module, not yet implemented) ---
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
